// SKIP: The spec models only typed d20 rolls (attack rolls via `resolveAttackRoll`, ability checks via `checkSucceeds`, saving throws via `saveSucceeds`, death saves via `pDeathSave`). The Q&A concerns "typeless" d20 rolls (e.g. wild magic surge) which have no representation in the spec, and neither True Polymorph nor the Duergar Warlord's Scouring Instruction reaction mechanic (add d6 to any d20 roll for 3 psychic damage) are modeled.